titleStmt.title: Where sundrie preachers haue latelie come into sundrie places of the diocesse of London, some of them not being ministers ...
titleStmt.author: Whitgift, John, 1530?-1604.

notesStmt.note: "Yeouen the XXvi. day of March in the yeare of our Lord God 1589."

At end of sheet: "Io: Cantuar. Ihon London. Tho. Winton. Harb. Hereford. Subsigned. Valen: Dale. Owyn Hopton. Bar: Clark. W. Aubrey. W. Fletewood. Edw. Stanhope. W. Lewyn. Ihon Mullins. Richard Cosin."
